data.description: Fantastic Opportunity!! This charming 3-bedroom, 2-and-1/2-bathroom end unit townhome nestled in the vibrant community of Oaks At Flat Shoals! This thoughtfully designed property offers a perfect blend of comfort, convenience, and modern elegance.    The kitchen is a focal point, boasting sleek granite countertops, stainless steel appliances, and ample cabinet space, inviting your inner chef to create culinary delights. A cozy breakfast nook or island seating offers a perfect spot to enjoy morning coffee or casual meals.    Upstairs, the master suite provides a tranquil retreat featuring generous space, a walk-in closet, and an en-suite bathroom, creating a private oasis for relaxation. Two additional well-appointed bedrooms share a stylishly designed full bathroom, catering to comfort and convenience for family members or guests.    A private concrete patio or backyard space invites outdoor gatherings, gardening, or simply unwinding in the fresh air.    Located in a sought-after community, residents enjoy access to various amenities.    This 3-bed, 2-and-1/2-bath end unit townhome offers a perfect combination of modern living and convenience, presenting an excellent opportunity to embrace a comfortable and sophisticated lifestyle.    Hurry and Bring your Offers!!! This home won't last long!!!
